the Weinstein deal. But =E2=80=9Ca number of clients raised concerns=E2=80=
=9D is not the same as =E2=80=9Cclients responsible for most of the assets =
said no.=E2=80=9D Sculptor does not seem to have systematically polled its =
clients, or gotten any definitive answers =E2=80=94=C2=A0just unspecified c=
oncerns from an unspecified number of clients.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The board, though, is not relying solely on an=
ecdotal feedback from the client relations team. It also hired a consultant=
