<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Between August 30, 2023 and Septem=
ber 13, 2023, representatives of the Asset Management Consultant took a ser=
ies of steps in connection with assisting the Special Committee in evaluati=
ng the Consortium Client Consent Condition Risk. These steps included, with=
out limitation, (i) arranging meetings with key investment professionals an=
d client relations professionals of the Company, (ii) undertaking an indepe=
ndent review of certain information provided by the Company, including with=
