-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">says =
Peter Brown</a>, the head of Renaissance Technologies, and he's not alone. =
Meanwhile those skills will still serve you well in=C2=A0acquiring, running=
 and selling a plumbing supply store.=C2=A0</p>
